node.text: Nova Babes, make sure you’ve got your headphones on because this game is definitely NSFW! We put Bri Martinez, Gia Gunn, and Jose Jimenez in the hot seat for a fun game of ‘What’s In The Box?’ that rivals any guessing game you’ve ever played. Their answers will have you SHOOK, trust us 😂 Watch this hilarious clip & tell us your favorite item in the comments👇 Watch the full video on our Youtube → https://youtu.be/rzOm3nToHi8

node.title: Can You Think Outside Of The Box? 😅📦

node.text:
Afternoon tea is too bougie. We’re all about getting tipsy and spilling the tea instead! Join @brimartinezz , @gia_gunn , and @laviedunprince as they take shots playing a fun drinking game called Purr Or Pass. And don’t forget to play along...if you dare 😈🥃(Drink responsibly).

Who will get the MOST drunk? You’ll have to watch the FULL Youtube video to find out 👉 https://youtu.be/WF53JPBozWQ

node.title: Tea Time But Make It Tipsy 🍵🍾
